":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":4206,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23955,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/31\/abu-darda-reconciliation\/","url_meta":{"origin":4206,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Virtue: No deeds better than prayer, good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Idris reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo deeds of the children of Adam are better than walking to prayer, having exceptional character, and reconciling people.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 725 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0633\u064e \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0631\u062f\u0627\u0621 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0622\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25336,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/25\/abu-darda-nifaq-khushu\/","url_meta":{"origin":4206,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Nifaq: Beware of hypocrisy of reverence, humility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Sa\u2019d reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the reverence of hypocrisy.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhat is the reverence of hypocrisy?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cIt is that you see the body in reverence, but the heart is not reverent.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/25\/abu-darda-salat-better-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":4206,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Taqwa: One accepted prayer better than entire world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Tamim ibn Malik reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThat I was certain Allah accepted even one prayer from me, it would be more beloved to me than the world and everything in it,\u00a0for Allah says: Verily, Allah only accepts from those who are righteous.\u201d\u00a0(5:27) Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/abu-darda-hate-his-sinful-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":4206,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Sinners: Hate his sinful deeds, do not abuse him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qilaba reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, passed by\u00a0a man who was being beaten because of his sin and they were cursing\u00a0him. Abu Darda\u00a0said, \u201cWhat do you think if he had fallen into a well. Would you not try to rescue him?\u201d They said yes.\u00a0Abu Darda\u00a0said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4206","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4206"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4206\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4206"}],"